Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.27,0:00:09.15,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}The American Industrial 30 Average \Nfell for the third day in a row,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.15,0:00:12.07,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,A,0000,0000,0000,,{\a6}marking the largest drop this year—
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.28,0:00:28.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,B,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel Boat has taken control \Nof 72% of all financial markets.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.60,0:00:31.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,Infrastructure is failing all over the place.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.38,0:00:34.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,C,0000,0000,0000,,We're losing control of the control circuits on our \Nweather satellites.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.79,0:00:36.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Relax.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.87,0:00:38.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,He's already on his way.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.47,0:01:02.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,Oh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.35,0:01:07.10,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,A human in our cyberspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.10,0:01:08.42,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,How rare.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.15,0:01:10.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the Angel Boat, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.15,0:01:15.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,That was our old name, the one we \Nused when we managed the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.16,0:01:18.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,We are now the gods that control
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.20,0:01:20.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,the real world!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.29,0:01:31.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,A mere human dived into cyberspace...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.59,0:01:34.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,An act akin to exposing their fragile psyche.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.33,0:01:36.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,I commend his bravery, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.21,0:01:40.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,You programs sure like to talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.83,0:01:50.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.91,0:01:52.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,TA,0000,0000,0000,,What did you do, human?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.39,0:01:54.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Giving a long speech \Nin front of your enemy...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.43,0:01:59.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,That's a death flag.
