Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.75,0:04:20.48,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Who's Souta-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.79,0:04:21.50,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.40,0:04:26.92,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I get it. \NYou're mad at Souta, too, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.92,0:04:29.93,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, sometimes we have to teach him a lesson.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.46,0:04:31.59,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:35.92,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Is Souta-kun a friend of yours, Nanami?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.92,0:04:36.79,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.03,0:04:40.34,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe you introduced me in the past?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.34,0:04:42.42,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry if I forgot.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.90,0:04:45.09,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-chan!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.55,0:04:47.68,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,A little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.19,0:04:51.27,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have a little brother.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.27,0:04:53.23,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,A male childhood friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.23,0:04:55.27,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,No, no one like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.63,0:04:58.25,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,The only guy at Quest Dorm?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.25,0:05:00.77,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,You're looking at him right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.77,0:05:02.93,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,The reason why I'm studying abroad?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.93,0:05:05.39,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,That's because I wanted to study
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.39,0:05:07.53,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,at the same school as you, I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.83,0:05:09.71,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Purple flag?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.03,0:05:11.55,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Who's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.40,0:05:17.79,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Okay,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.79,0:05:20.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,let's get homeroom started.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.13,0:05:24.05,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Right here!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.31,0:05:25.98,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.98,0:05:27.44,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This is Souta's room!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.51,0:05:30.11,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Calm down.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.43,0:05:33.22,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Did you forget that this room was locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.83,0:05:35.12,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Locked?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.12,0:05:35.68,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.68,0:05:36.94,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.94,0:05:39.33,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-oneechan fell through the floor in
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.33,0:05:41.65,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,the room and there was this big accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.88,0:05:45.53,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Luckily, Mahougasawa-kun was uninjured.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.53,0:05:47.80,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,But the place is still dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.29,0:05:49.60,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,We closed it off.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.56,0:05:53.66,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sure you're tired after the fair.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.29,0:05:57.27,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.80,0:06:03.34,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.82,0:06:06.82,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback_Italics,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,That's not what happened...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.95,0:06:32.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back, Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.20,0:06:33.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Sotua,0000,0000,0000,,Fall back?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.20,0:06:36.62,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The network in that area \Ncan no longer be used.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.43,0:06:40.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven Virtues used \Ninformation warfare to watch over the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.75,0:06:42.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and occasionally, direct it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.51,0:06:45.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You could say that the world is centered \Naround the Principality of Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.71,0:06:48.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,In conclusion, as long as this country exists,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.57,0:06:50.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,then the world shall not perish.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.04,0:06:52.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta, protect the world,
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.26,0:06:54.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,protect Bladefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.51,0:07:03.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Behind you rests the main server
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.49,0:07:05.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,for the Principality of Bladefield,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.20,0:07:09.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,and if it is destroyed, \Nthen the world will end. Period.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.80,0:07:12.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,The virtual worlds are no exception.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.99,0:07:13.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The virtual worlds...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.40,0:07:26.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,How amusingly simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.82,0:07:33.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let a
Dialogue: 0,0:07:34.72,0:07:36.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,single one of you through!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.92,0:08:07.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going to protect them!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.43,0:08:30.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I won't let it all
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.28,0:08:33.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,end now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.85,0:08:43.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Happy graduation!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.70,0:08:46.29,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.76,0:08:49.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,But while I'm happy, I'm also a little sad.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.12,0:08:52.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, we're not just saying goodbye to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.45,0:08:54.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,but to Quest Dorm, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.63,0:08:57.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it was set to be demolished \Nonce you graduated...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.53,0:09:00.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it makes sense given \Nthe incident with Akane.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.14,0:09:05.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I know we might not want to leave,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:07.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,but let's get going.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.79,0:09:09.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,To new pastures!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.37,0:09:17.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,I know it's weird to be asking this now,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.46,0:09:20.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,but why were we all living \Nin this dorm, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.45,0:09:22.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,That's a good point.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.59,0:09:24.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,It's far from school,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.05,0:09:25.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,and it's a pain to commute every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.88,0:09:28.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but it was home to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.09,0:09:36.09,Kanojo_Flag_Flashback,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I won't live here unless \NI get that corner room!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.71,0:09:50.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Akane-chan?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.96,0:09:52.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe she forgot something?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.04,0:09:55.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Forgot something...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.17,0:10:02.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stand not solving
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.90,0:10:04.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,any mystery
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.87,0:10:07.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,that catches
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.50,0:10:11.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,my eye!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.82,0:10:37.82,letter_10:35,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,To Hatate Souta
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.79,0:10:37.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,A letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.90,0:10:46.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,What's up with this letter?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.66,0:10:49.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,This is my handwriting...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.03,0:10:50.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami-san.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.62,0:10:52.47,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.59,0:10:55.93,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.48,0:11:00.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't think you'd break through \NSouta-san's protection mechanism.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.37,0:11:01.66,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Protection mechanism?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.96,0:11:04.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You remember Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.96,0:11:10.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you back everything \NI've been keeping.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.25,0:11:11.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.68,0:11:25.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Where am...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.84,0:11:27.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,It's been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.02,0:11:31.13,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Who are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.13,0:11:32.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Me?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.89,0:11:34.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Souta's older sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.53,0:11:36.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Nanami.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:47.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You're...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.31,0:11:51.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Have your memories not fully \Nsynchronized yet?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.77,0:11:54.96,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No, they're still a little fuzzy.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.32,0:11:56.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,But
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.27,0:12:00.04,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I never would have thought that this \Nwas a virtual world on a network,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.04,0:12:03.09,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and that Souta was my
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.09,0:12:04.78,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,brother in the real world...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.38,0:12:06.68,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,It's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.68,0:12:08.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,You were so close, that you followed him
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.65,0:12:10.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,to this virtual world because you were worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.46,0:12:14.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,The Angel Boat, located in
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.24,0:12:17.21,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,the real world, staged a \Nrevolt against humanity.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.21,0:12:19.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven \NVirtues went into action,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.27,0:12:21.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,and that was the start of everything.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.79,0:12:23.41,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why the Council of the Seven Virtues?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.41,0:12:26.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,They're only a special \Norganization within Bladefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.94,0:12:29.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,That's only what they wanted \Neveryone to think. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.86,0:12:32.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I'm starting to remember.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.83,0:12:34.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The Council of the Seven Virtues is a
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.76,0:12:37.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,secret organization that controlled \Nthe world's information networks,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.26,0:12:39.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,through which the Bladefield Principality was
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.45,0:12:40.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,manipulated into becoming a greater global power.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.16,0:12:43.48,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Of course they couldn't allow the
Dialogue: 0,0:12:43.48,0:12:45.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Angel Boat to take over the network.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.17,0:12:50.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,And that's when Number Zero \Ntook notice of Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.33,0:12:53.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why would they try to use the prince \Nof the country which they serve?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.20,0:12:56.33,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,The fairy tale told in the Principality.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.55,0:12:57.23,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.93,0:12:59.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,All of that was true.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.58,0:13:01.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,The founder,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.84,0:13:04.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Kagura Bladefield, was said to \Nbe a descendant of one of the
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.77,0:13:06.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,heroic female knights who \Nfought against the demons
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.98,0:13:09.24,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,and the man that had turned into the flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.24,0:13:11.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,It is said that every \Ngeneration the royal family
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:13.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,has someone born with superhuman powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.35,0:13:15.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Souta?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.83,0:13:18.90,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Number Zero connected Souta's consciousness
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.90,0:13:20.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,with several virtual worlds,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.80,0:13:23.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,and through a massive amount of simulations,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.02,0:13:25.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,tried activating his superhuman powers.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.52,0:13:27.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,So I went into the virtual \Nworlds trying to save Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.25,0:13:30.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Trying to save my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.96,0:13:33.51,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.51,0:13:35.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,But Number Zero detected what you
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.92,0:13:37.77,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,were doing, and interfered,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.77,0:13:40.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,and we... we were separated \Ninto two sets of data.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.18,0:13:44.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,And so I was imprisoned \Nin this virtual world.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.19,0:13:48.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And I was made into her pawn—his classmate.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.44,0:13:52.72,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I know I'm just trying \Nto recall what happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.72,0:13:54.37,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,but I'm started to get mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.37,0:13:55.43,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Me, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.43,0:13:58.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,But there was something she couldn't prevent.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.73,0:13:59.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,That's where...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.02,0:14:02.26,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,...I came in.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.26,0:14:03.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.52,0:14:07.15,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,I managed to escape from \Nmy imprisonment, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.95,0:14:12.91,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,While I was configuring the \Nprogram that would save Souta...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.60,0:14:20.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,I ran low on power.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:22.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,I found Ruri's body by accident,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.97,0:14:26.28,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,and I guess you could say I borrowed it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.69,0:14:31.74,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, I couldn't say anything
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.74,0:14:33.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,and slept within her.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.24,0:14:36.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,But as a result, there was a
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.58,0:14:38.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,new personality, a new "Ruri" born,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.92,0:14:40.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and my thoughts and emotions were,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.88,0:14:43.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,albeit faintly, sketched into her AI,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.14,0:14:45.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,so that she would help Souta out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.52,0:14:50.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, I guess it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.62,0:14:53.03,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Now that our synchronization has finished,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.34,0:14:55.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,it's time for us to become one.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.02,0:14:56.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,That is what is to be.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.34,0:14:58.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,But more importantly,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.97,0:15:02.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Souta is alone, fighting away in cyberspace
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.01,0:15:03.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,where time has no meaning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.97,0:15:05.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,We must save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.26,0:15:07.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,And we will,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.58,0:15:11.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,with the heroes who brandish the Royal Flag—\Nthose that care for Souta dearly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.26,0:15:19.06,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I remember everything now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.37,0:15:23.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Why I patterned everything \Nafter the fairy tale...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.40,0:15:26.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,The fairy tale we heard from our mother.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.96,0:15:29.52,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,We shed tears hearing the fate \Nof the man who became the flag,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.89,0:15:31.53,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and talked about it together...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.69,0:15:37.45,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,No matter how cliché, \Nhow deus ex machina it feels,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.69,0:15:41.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,it's better to have a happy ending \Nrather than a moving, bitter one.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.35,0:15:46.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,Let us go then, you and I—us.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.19,0:15:48.02,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.32,0:15:49.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Together,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.63,0:15:51.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,to...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.74,0:15:53.64,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami2,0000,0000,0000,,...Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.97,0:16:09.20,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Ruri, could you help me?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.48,0:16:12.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Do I need to answer that?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.47,0:16:14.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.73,0:16:17.67,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.23,0:16:21.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,I... I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.68,0:16:24.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,It feels like I've forgotten \Nsomething important,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.28,0:16:28.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,but I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.04,0:16:31.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Akane...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.44,0:16:38.05,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to save him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.98,0:16:50.32,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think I wouldn't listen to a
Dialogue: 0,0:16:50.32,0:16:52.61,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,request made by my best friend?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.31,0:17:00.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.09,0:17:07.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.10,0:17:23.76,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,What's in this thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.76,0:17:24.60,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Who knows...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.86,0:17:26.75,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:26.75,0:17:29.83,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,There's only one reason \NI've brought you all here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.13,0:17:31.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I want you to
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.70,0:17:34.36,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,help my younger brother, Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.36,0:17:37.97,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,That's the guy you've been \Ntalking about, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.97,0:17:39.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Your brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.12,0:17:40.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,Indeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.12,0:17:44.12,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,I heard that both you Nanami and \NHakua are only siblings.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.40,0:17:45.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,,0000,0000,0000,,No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.46,0:17:49.46,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,You mean Father had adulterous relations in the thick steam of the hot spring, he did?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.91,0:17:53.88,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,He'd be your older brother, Hakua.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.46,0:17:56.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-sama?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.13,0:18:00.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,So he means a lot to you, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.33,0:18:03.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Yes,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.19,0:18:06.70,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,and to all of you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.58,0:18:12.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,That just means
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.01,0:18:14.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,we'll have to help!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.65,0:18:19.57,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, there's no reason not to help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.83,0:18:22.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Just let my manliness take care of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.08,0:18:27.08,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.83,0:18:32.84,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I thank you all!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.11,0:18:50.40,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,How could I forget someone so important...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.50,0:18:52.48,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Sou-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:54.27,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.64,0:18:55.65,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.08,0:18:57.40,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,Little Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.36,0:18:59.91,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate Souta.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.58,0:19:01.87,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Onii-chan.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.40,0:19:03.50,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.90,0:19:05.87,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Souta-oniisama.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.76,0:19:07.87,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.61,0:19:09.70,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Hatate...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.92,0:19:19.63,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Safety release confirmed!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.63,0:19:22.59,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,This is our final hope which \NNanami-san has entrusted us!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.59,0:19:25.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like to activate the \Ndimensional tracing program?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.14,0:19:26.49,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Yes or no?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.49,0:19:27.35,Kanojo_Flag_Main,All,0000,0000,0000,,Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.83,0:19:40.99,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,You're more perfect than I imagined.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.56,0:19:43.86,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,I couldn't expect more from a \Ndescendant of the Royal Flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.75,0:19:48.18,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Fight as long as you live!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.18,0:19:49.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,Fight for our world.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.55,0:19:53.50,Kanojo_Flag_Main,No0,0000,0000,0000,,No, for our homeland, for Bladefield!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.71,0:20:11.71,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I've come this far and now the \Ndefeat flag shows itself?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.21,0:20:13.98,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is just a fake ocean...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:13.98,0:20:14.65,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,This is nothing!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.15,0:20:25.09,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,I need to break them...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.49,0:20:28.66,Kanojo_Flag_Italics,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Break them now.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.76,0:20:35.82,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.56,0:20:37.55,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.89,0:20:48.39,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,The Premium Ambriel...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.20,0:21:06.92,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,I guess this would be \Nthe reinforcements flag.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.17,0:21:12.58,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,N-Nanami!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.09,0:21:16.25,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,It can't be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.20,0:21:18.27,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:20.75,0:21:24.11,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Your older sister and her \Nmerry band of friends have arrived!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.91,0:23:12.95,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.95,0:23:14.22,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Akane,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.22,0:23:15.16,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kikuno,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.43,0:23:16.73,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Megumu,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:16.73,0:23:17.85,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Ruri,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.85,0:23:19.00,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Rin,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:19.00,0:23:20.19,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mimori,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.19,0:23:21.38,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Tsumugu,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.38,0:23:22.56,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Mei,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.56,0:23:23.80,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Kurumiko,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.80,0:23:24.87,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Hakua,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.87,0:23:26.01,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Serika,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.01,0:23:27.14,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Miyuki,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.14,0:23:28.34,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Souta,0000,0000,0000,,Roar! Gawo!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.64,0:23:31.30,Kanojo_Flag_Main,Nanami,0000,0000,0000,,And all of us together...
